nada para fazer,

00:38:43.999 --> 00:38:46.399
quer tomar um milk-shake
no Pop's?

00:38:48.335 --> 00:38:51.436
- Tem certeza?
- Sim.

00:38:52.239 --> 00:38:54.005
Betty, eu adoraria.

00:38:59.613 --> 00:39:03.748
